<!---DOCTYPE html--->
<html>
<head>
     <!--adding style sheets and fonts-->
     <link rel="stylesheet" href="../assets/css/style.css" type="text/css">
     <link rel="stylesheet" href="../assets/css/all.css" type="text/css">
     <script src="https://ajax.googleapis.com/ajax/libs/jquery/3.5.1/jquery.min.js"></script>
     <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com">
     <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Antic&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
     <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Oswald:wght@200;300&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
     <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Quattrocento:wght@400;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
     <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Montserrat:wght@400;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <title>iVideo</title>
    <!--adding icon to title-->
    <link rel="icon" href="../assets/img/logo.png" >
</head>
<body>
    <div class="fhalf">
        <!--adding navigation bar-->
        <div class="banner">
            <div class="bannerwrapper">
                <img src="../assets/img/banner.jpg" alt="banner_image">
            </div>
            <div class="bannertext">
                <img class="applogo" src="../assets/img/logo.png" alt="applogo here">
                <div class="apptext">AUTOMATED VIDEO GENERATOR</div>
                <div class="apptagline">Easy & Faster</div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <button id="quick_download">Quick Download</button>
    </div>


    <!--second section of the code-->
    
        
    <div class="shalf">

        <div class="sectionDescription">
            <div class="subheading">perfect time to</div>
            <div class="mainheading">Create new video!</div>
        </div>
        <div class="method_holder">
            <div class="method_img_wrapper">
                <img src="../assets/img/methodimg.png" alt="upload image icon">
            </div>
            <div class="methoddescription">
                <p>Video production is always a fascinating thing to do. But at the same time it is difficult without experience. Here you can create video for your presentation, project or meetings with some simple clicks. So here we are to upload image and description, Create video using them!</p>
                <form method="GET" action="/createvideo">
                    <input type="submit" id="upimg" value="Create Now">
                </form>
            </div>
        </div>

    </div>
     <!--How to make-->

     <section class="how_to_do">
         <div class="section_header">
             How It Works!
         </div>
         <div class="steps">
             <div class="step">
                 <div class="step_heading">
                     <i class="fas fa-filter"></i>
                     <h3>Choose Category</h3>
                </div>
                <p>
                    Choose the category in which your data belongs. if you don't find it on the list add new category using add more option.
                </p>
             </div>
             <div class="step">
                <div class="step_heading">
                    <i class="fas fa-sticky-note"></i>
                    <h3>Validate Filename</h3>
               </div>
               <p>
                   Select an available filename. This file name can be used for future references, and quick download.
               </p>
            </div>
            <div class="step">
                <div class="step_heading">
                    <i class="fas fa-angle-up"></i>
                    <h3>Upload Images</h3>
               </div>
               <p>
                   Upload images of same dimension named in order of their appearence into the server using the upload button. 
               </p>
            </div>
            <div class="step">
                <div class="step_heading">
                    <i class="fas fa-music"></i>
                    <h3>Create Background Track</h3>
               </div>
               <p>
                   Type the text that you need to covert to audio into the text area. If you don't need audio, still you have to click the create audio button to move forward.
               </p>
            </div>
            <div class="step">
                <div class="step_heading">
                    <i class="fas fa-film"></i>
                    <h3>Add Frame</h3>
               </div>
               <p>
                   Click on the Add Frame button to create new frame. You have to give a fps value also. It will take some time depending upon the file size.
               </p>
            </div>
            <div class="step">
                <div class="step_heading">
                    <i class="fas fa-wave-square"></i>
                    <h3>Render</h3>
               </div>
               <p>
                   Press the Render button to make video from frames. After completion you can download the video.
               </p>
            </div>
            <div class="image_wrapper">
                <img src="../assets/img/logo.png" alt="howtouseimage">
            </div>
         </div>

     </section>


    <!--adding modal popup-->
    
    <div class="QD_modal_bg">
        
        <div class="qd_modalpopup">
            
            <div class="qd_close">+</div>
            <div class="qdicon_wrapper">
                <img src="../assets/img/logo.png" alt=appicon>
            </div><br>
            <p id="app">iVideo</p>
            <i class="fas fa-download"></i>
            <form class="deatails" action="/quickdownload" method="POST">
                <p>Download video created by you or your colleague using a valid file name</p>
                <input type="text" id="video_name" name="videofname" placeholder="Video file name" autocomplete="off"><br>
                <button id="qkdwd" type="submit" disabled="disabled">Download File</button>
            </form>
            
        </div>
     </div>
    
    
    
